  2347                                  ;       Routine:        FirstConsoleColumn
  2348                                  ;
  2349                                  ;       Description:    This routine resets the console column to start of the row.
  2350                                  ;
  2351                                  ;       In:             DS      OS data selector
  2352                                  ;
  2353                                  ;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
