  2496                                  ;       Routine:        PutConsoleOIAShift
  2497                                  ;
  2498                                  ;       Description:    This routine updates the shift/ctrl/alt/lock indicators in the operator information area (OIA).
  2499                                  ;
  2500                                  ;       In:             BL      shift flags
